        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "He is a born sportsman and loves an open air life-a warrior, always ready to accept battle, but seldom provoking it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "He has a way of his own with tramps, and seldom fails to induce them to continue their travels.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "In China, his fatherland, he is esteemed for another quality-his excellence as a substitute for roast mutton.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Though in his own country he is regarded as plebeian, just a common cur, he is by no means a mongrel.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "That he is of ancient lineage is proved by the fact that he always breeds true to type.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "If you doubt it, look at his tongue.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Outwardly, the Chow worthily embodies the kind, faithful heart and the brave spirit within.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000006_000002",
