        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "His handsome face wears a \"scowl.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "This is the technical term for the \"no nonsense\" look which deters strangers from undue familiarity, though to friends his expression is kindness itself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Though the Chow has many perfections, the perfect Chow has not yet arrived.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "With many judges, however, this dog's black coat handicaps him sadly in competition with his red brethren.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Almond eyes are of course correct in Chinamen.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14900_000007_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14900/4310_14900_000007_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Red Craze owns the head which is perfect with the correct ear carriage and broad muzzle, and the scowl and characteristic expression of a good Chow.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
