        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "The Newmarket Meeting in eighteen o five was the next fixture that was inaugurated, and this now remains with the champion stakes as its most important event.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000006_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000006_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Afterwards came the Amesbury Meeting in eighteen twenty two, but Amesbury, like Ashdown, although for many years one of the most celebrated institutions of the description, has fallen from its high estate.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000006_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000006_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Three years later came the Altcar Club.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000006_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000006_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "But it was not until eleven years after this period that the Waterloo Cup was instituted (in eighteen thirty six), to win which is the highest ambition of followers of the leash.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "This is recognised in Australia and other parts of the world where coursing meetings are held.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "In fact, the National Coursing Club is more particular in connection with the pedigrees of Greyhounds being correctly given, than the Kennel Club is about dogs that are exhibited; and that is saying a great deal. It holds the same position in coursing matters as the Jockey Club does in racing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "It is in fact, the supreme authority on all matters connected with coursing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Coomassie was the smallest Greyhound that ever won the blue ribbon of the leash; she drew the scale at forty two pounds., and was credited with the win of the Cup on two occasions.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Bab at the Bowster, who is considered by many good judges to have been the best bitch that ever ran, was two pounds.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000009_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000009_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Master McGrath was a small dog, and only weighed fifty three pounds., but he won the Waterloo Cup three times.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
