        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000009_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Fullerton, who was a much bigger dog, and was four times declared the winner of the Cup, was fifty six pounds. in weight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "He ran five times altogether for the Waterloo Cup, and was declared the winner on four occasions. The first time was in eighteen eighty nine, when he divided with his kennel companion Troughend.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "This was one of the two occasions upon which out of thirty three courses he failed to raise the flag.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4310_14908_000011_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4310/14908/4310_14908_000011_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "On the other he was beaten by mr Gladstone's Greengage, when running the deciding course at Haydock Park.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
