        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "Although, as a rule, the most consistent winners in the leash have not been noted for their good looks, there have been exceptions in which the opposite has been the case.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
