        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4310",
        "content": "In the South of England mrs a Dewe keeps a number of longtails that when not winning prizes at the Crystal Palace and elsewhere are running at Plumpton and other meetings in Sussex.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
